== [[Asemmili]] uffiɣ ==
Am wazal ameqran n ibureɣsen, Tafekka n ufaylellis igber seg 3 n wamuren igejdanen, yal amur yettaddam tagrawt n yigmanen<ref name="Anatomy"/><ref>[http://encarta.msn.com/media_461543522/Characteristics_of_a_Moth.html Tiskanin n ifaylellisen] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090507002039/http://encarta.msn.com/media_461543522/Characteristics_of_a_Moth.html |date=7 mayyu 2009}}</ref>.

* '''Ixef''': yettili ɣervzdat n tfekka, igber seg wallen deg wadisen d [[timejjiwin]] i d-izgan gar n wallen, Timejjiwin-a ttusmersent s talɣa tagejdant i ugerrew tekdiwin d usekdu (alqaḍ n rrwayeḥ d wesfuḥu) acku gant d tinafrayin i [[tanga|tnegwa]] [[takrura|tikruranin]] deg igenni. Akken i yella yimi yakk d yiles yecban tasummut  ɣezzifen, ɣef wanecta i tegguni deg wučči ɣef [[amɣus|wemɣus]] n yijeǧǧigen d tnegwa [[amazzal|timazzalin]].
* '''Idmaren''': D tama i d-izgan gar n yixef d wadis, itedden sin n wafriwen, maca llant kra n [[tawtemt|twetmin]] ur lint ara aya.
* '''Adis''': D amur n deffir i d-izgan deffir n yidmaren, itedden azal meqqren n yigmanen d yinagrawen ixataren deg tfekka n ufaylellis, gar-asen [[anagraw amaẓẓad]] d unazzuf yakk d yildiyen n usnezwi ixeddmen am [[anagraw amesgunef|unagraw amesgunef]].

